{"tid":362171,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[傷心事]我太天真了","createTime":"2017-08-16T17:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T20:52:23.000Z","uid":45185,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa19e9153133a8abfdecfde47824396faf9bb961","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"我成日都覺得相/影片同埋啲對話紀錄係回憶,<br />\n<br />\n但真正既player手機入面一定係好乾淨得啲正經既野,<br />\n<br />\n真真正正唔見得光既野,例如閃卡一早已經者backup左起你絕對唔會搵到既地方,<br />\n<br />\n再加上佢老練既經驗,放低部手機去廁所,當你見到入面啲聯絡人同對話紀錄所有野都好正常,覺得好安心,<br />\n<br />\n到最後佢離開你先發現<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你又上左一堂</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以無需要對任何人上心,啱唔啱聽先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35238825e3af8929193107c8fadf0521b6f649c","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:27:23.000Z","msg":"得正皮冇人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d40cf7985f38033a066920c005733e94ae495a1","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f223a02e08ea2e8c5d5369fa8ecafb5a79786ff","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:32:21.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4198a455bdd02a900b8b5d846210c9545dad224","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:32:34.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9928995c291db22b8587b7aaee1e7e4244beae7","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T17:32:44.000Z","msg":"6<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d0245dad03c0070fe41647636b3633a68f670","tid":362171,"uid":45185,"li